      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat(ux): UX-007 + UX-008 — board drag + shortcut legend [sprint 2 closeout]",
        "body": "## Changes\n\n### UX-007 — Board card drag between columns\n- Adds `workboard-card--dragging` class (opacity 0.4 + purple box-shadow) to the source card during drag\n- Activates existing `.workboard-column--drop` dashed-outline styling on all valid drop targets\n- Native HTML5 drag scaffolding (dragstart/dragend/dragover/drop + moveWorkboardCard) was already in place; this completes the ghost/overlay visual polish\n\n### UX-008 — ? keyboard shortcut legend\n- Press `?` anywhere (outside text inputs) to open/toggle the legend overlay\n- Grouped shortcuts: Navigation · Chat · Board/Workboard · General\n- Glass surface panel (`var(--panel)` + backdrop blur), focus-trapped (Tab cycles within), `Esc` to close\n- ARIA: `role=\"dialog\"`, `aria-modal`, `aria-label=\"Keyboard shortcuts\"`\n- Responsive 2-col layout collapses to 1-col on mobile\n- New `shortcut-legend.css` file imported in `styles.css`\n\n---\nPart of UI/UX Enhancement Sprint 2.",
